                   AMODE and RMODE validation


The binder validates the AMODE and RMODE combination according to the
following table:

                RMODE=24   RMODE=ANY    RMODE=64

AMODE=24        valid      invalid      invalid
AMODE=31        valid      valid        invalid
AMODE=ANY       valid      invalid      invalid
AMODE=64        valid      valid        valid
